{"tid":927423,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"其實城市根本大部分人都係孤獨","createTime":"2018-12-04T07:00:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-04T07:03:12.000Z","uid":58335,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"77a97355753e8300de83b854e33f079665046d2f","tid":927423,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T07:00:01.000Z","msg":"你以為你有另一半就唔係孤獨啦咩？<br />\n有幾多所謂情侶甚至結婚<br />\n都係因為想搵個人做伴同張長期飯票先結婚<br />\n根本就唔係真愛<br />\n<br />\n你以為你有朋友就唔係孤獨啦咩？<br />\n好多人根本為利益而走埋一齊<br />\n當你真係有事要搵佢幫手<br />\n甚至只係傾訴下心事<br />\n就會人影都唔見咗<br />\n<br />\n結論係根本眾人都是孤獨的<br />\n所以民至老死不相往來，先係最好解決/適應孤獨既方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺醒吧連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de5dd499d07ba9b6e062e095855674e2783dfdd3","tid":927423,"uid":141901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T07:02:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afb01b6fa9079cb2645b9bb3cb9ed0961afc6bfa","tid":927423,"uid":141901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T07:03:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </blockquote><br />\n自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}